						<summary>

						<p>Stone found in the local temple of Śiva called Gartēśvara.</p>						

						<p>Anantavarma [Chōḍagaṅga].</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">23rd year, ba. • • • Traya-ēkadasi, Sunday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Mentions Vishṇuvardhana Vijayādityadēva Chakravarti, Lokamahādēvi and Rājarāja and records some gift to the god Guṟtta-dēva at Arugumaguṭṭa.</p>						

